termreadkey: A perl module for simple terminal control
termreadkey:
termreadkey: This module, ReadKey, provides ioctl control for terminals
termreadkey: and Win32 consoles so the input modes can be changed (thus
termreadkey: allowing reads of a single character at a time), and also
termreadkey: provides non-blocking reads of stdin, as well as several other
termreadkey: terminal related features, including retrieval/modification
termreadkey: of the screen size, and retrieval/modification of the control
termreadkey: characters.
